title: Call Girl Wives (2005)(BustyJana)
description:
Director: Michael Whiteacre
Writers: Michael Whiteacre (story), Patrick Hobby (screenplay)
Stars: Shyla Stylez, Taimie Hannum and Ashley Long

Story:
Three young housewives, feeling neglected and abandoned after their spouses go off together on their latest hunting trip, try out at an elite brothel run by the glamorous Madam Brittany for kicks and cash. But what begins as a sexy lark takes on greater consequences, and soon becomes a life-changing experience for the sexy trio -- especially once the dark secret shared by their patronizing, inattentive husbands is revealed. 

Happy Fapping Bitches!
